<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1170571652896">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1170571652898">
<p id="fs-id1170571652901">An engineer is using a machine to cut a flat square of Aerogel of area 144 cm<sup>2</sup>. If there is a maximum error tolerance in the area of 8 cm<sup>2</sup>, how accurately must the engineer cut on the side, assuming all sides have the same length? How do these numbers relate to <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>&#948;</mi><mo>,</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>&#948;</mi><mo>,</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> <em data-effect="italics">&#949;</em>, <em data-effect="italics">a</em>, and <em data-effect="italics">L</em>?</p>
</div>
<div data-type="solution" id="fs-id1170571652930">
<p id="fs-id1170571652932">0.033 cm, <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>&#949;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>&#948;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.33</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>144</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>&#949;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>&#948;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.33</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>12</mn><mo>,</mo><mi>L</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>144</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
</div>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1170572551905">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1170572551907">
<p id="fs-id1170572551909">Use the precise definition of limit to prove that the following limit does not exist: <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><munder><mrow><mtext>lim</mtext></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">&#8594;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mrow><mo>|</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>|</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>.</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><munder><mrow><mtext>lim</mtext></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">&#8594;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mrow><mo>|</mo><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>|</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>.</mo></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
