</span>
</div>
</div>
<p id="fs-id1170572330119">In the following exercises, evaluate the limit algebraically or explain why the limit does not exist.</p>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1170572330123">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1170572330125">
<p id="fs-id1170572330128"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><munder><mrow><mtext>lim</mtext></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">&#8594;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><munder><mrow><mtext>lim</mtext></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">&#8594;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></munder><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>&#8722;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
