<p id="fs-id1170572601279">In the following exercises, use the squeeze theorem to prove the limit.</p>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1170572601282">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1170572601284">
<p id="fs-id1170572601287"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><munder><mrow><mtext>lim</mtext></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">&#8594;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mtext>cos</mtext><mspace width="0.1em"/><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&#960;</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><munder><mrow><mtext>lim</mtext></mrow><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy="false">&#8594;</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></munder><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mtext>cos</mtext><mspace width="0.1em"/><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>&#960;</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
